ENTRY            31872   20260213   20260508   20260508       3222
SUBENT        31872001   20260213   20260508   20260508       3222
BIB                 14         32
TITLE      Measurement of spectral averaged cross sections of
            capture reactions in the LR-0 reference neutron field
AUTHOR     (E.Losa, M.Kostal, J.Simon, T.Czakoj)
INSTITUTE  (3CZRUJV)
REFERENCE  (J,ARI,210,111351,2024)
FACILITY   (REAC,3CZRUJV) LR-0 reactor at the research centre Rez,
            using VVER-1000 fuel
INC-SOURCE (REAC)
DETECTOR   (HPGE) Efficiency calculated by MCNP6
METHOD     (ACTIV)
MONITOR    (79-AU-197(N,G)79-AU-198,,SIG)
            (3.6 mm diameter, 0.1 mm thickness)
           (28-NI-58(N,P)27-CO-58,,SIG)
            (10 X 10 X 0.1 mm)
           (26-FE-54(N,P)25-MN-54,,SIG)
            (10 X 10 X 3 mm)
           (73-TA-181(N,G)73-TA-182,,SIG)
            (3.6 mm diameter, 0.1 mm thickness)
DECAY-MON  (25-MN-54,312.2D,DG,834.8,0.9998)
           (73-TA-182-G,114.74D,DG,1121.3,0.3524,
                                DG,1221.4,0.2723)
CORRECTION corrected for:
           . coincidence summing factor
           . resonance shielding
           . detector efficiency
ERR-ANALYS (ERR-T) Uncertainty propagated from
           (ERR-S,,2.) counting statistics (<2%)
           (ERR-1,,3.) scaling factor (<3%)
           (ERR-2) detector efficiency (1.8%)
STATUS     (APRVD) Proof-read by Michal Kostal (2026-02-16)
           (TABLE,,E.Losa+,J,ARI,210,111351,2024) Table 9
HISTORY    (20260213C) VT
ENDBIB              32
COMMON               2          3
EN-DUMMY   ERR-2
MEV        PER-CENT
         1.        1.8
ENDCOMMON            3
ENDSUBENT           39
